Title: Brain scRNA-seq data, 'RLE-compressed'
Description: Single-cell RNA-seq data for 1.3 million brain cells from E18 mice. 'RLE-compressed' format originally provided by TENx Genomics

Title: Brain scRNA-seq data, 'rectangular'
Description: Single-cell RNA-seq data for 1.3 million brain cells from E18 mice. Full rectangular, block-compressed format, 1GB block size.

Title: Brain scRNA-seq data, sample (column) annotation
Description: Single-cell RNA-seq data for 1.3 million brain cells from E18 mice. Inferred sample descriptions.

Title: Brain scRNA-seq data, gene (row) annotation
Description: Single-cell RNA-seq data for 1.3 million brain cells from E18 mice. Gene descriptions.
